  2             pounds  penne

Melt the butter in a large pot and stir in the tomato paste mixture.  Bring the mixture to a boil, then lower the heat and slowly stir in the cream and vodka.  Stir in the cheese and taste for salt.  Keep the sauce warm while the penne cooks.

